        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 17 at 4:02PM MDT until July 17 at 4:30PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 401 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Gildford, or 25
miles east of Chester, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Gildford, Hingham, and Kremlin.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
